---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Turbomachinery Research - Fluid Innovation Lab',
  description: 'Understanding extreme events in turbomachines through advanced imaging and flow control techniques.',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};

const project = {
  title: 'Turbomachinery Research',
  summary: 'Understand the Extreme Events in Turbomachines',
  image: '/images/projects/7.png',
  additionalImages: [
    {
      src: '/images/projects/8.png',
      caption: 'Stall delaying by casing grooves'
    },
    {
      src: '/images/projects/9.png',
      caption: 'Complex vortex structure in the tip region of a turbomachine'
    },
    {
      src: '/images/projects/10.png',
      caption: 'Cavitation inside an axial waterjet pump'
    }
  ],
  content: `
Stall, surge, and cavitation are all extreme events that are detrimental to the performance of turbomachines. We use sophisticated imaging techniques to look into the complex flow fields to understand the causes of these events. Later, we use advanced flow control techniques to mitigate their effects. Figure 1 shows how casing grooves can help delay the onset of stall, Figure 2 shows the complex vortical structure measured by 3D PIV, and Figure 3 shows an axial waterjet pump experiencing severe cavitation.
  `
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-teal-400">
        {project.title}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-muted dark:text-slate-400">
        {project.summary}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Main Image -->
      <div class="mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <img
          src={project.image}
          alt={project.title}
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mx-auto">
        <p class="whitespace-pre-line">{project.content}</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Additional Images -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
          {project.additionalImages.map((img, index) => (
            <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
              <img
                src={img.src}
                alt={`${project.title} - Visualization ${index + 2}`}
                class="w-full h-auto"
              />
              <div class="p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
                <p class="text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">{img.caption}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 